SUMMARY:Masako Miki: Shapeshifters\, Sprites\, and Spirits
DTSTAMP:20260630T134651Z
DTSTART:20260711T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:This exhibition is curated by Associate Curator Claudia Mattos 
	with Suzanne Deal Booth Executive Director Alison Weaver and is made possi
	ble by the City of Houston through the Houston Arts Alliance\, the Moody C
	enter for the Arts Excellence Fund\, the H. Russell Pitman Fund for the Mo
